'''''tamar''''' is an [[Adûnaic]] word meaning "smith".<ref>{{SD|Nouns}}, p. 436</ref>

In an earlier version of what would later become the chapter [[A Journey in the Dark]], [[Berúthiel]] is referred to as '''Tamar'''.<ref>{{RS|4XXVN}}, p. 454 and p. 464 note 26</ref>

